The Sega theme has been installed.

In order to activate the theme, follow the procedures outlined under the following links:
- https://connectwww.com/how-to-install-plymouth-themes-in-ubuntu-customize-the-boot-splash-screen-in-ubuntu/60731/
- https://fedoramagazine.org/howto-change-the-plymouth-theme/
- https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/plymouth#Changing_the_Theme 

Alternatively, run the following command:
	sudo ln -s /usr/share/plymouth/themes/sega/sega.plymouth /usr/share/plymouth/themes/default.plymouth && sudo update-initramfs -u
